'''Nether Darkness''' refers to the far south of flat [[Arda]]. In the [[Second Age]], the [[Númenóreans]] reached the Nether Darkness by sea.<ref>{{S|Akallabeth}}</ref> It was probably uninhabited and, as the name suggests, apparently unlit by the [[Sun]] and [[Moon]].<ref>{{HM|Guide}}, entry "Nether Darkness"</ref>
